snippet.title: Unreal Tournament 2004 Full Game 10-hour Longplay Walkthrough "Godlike" 1080p HD
snippet.description:
Unreal Tournament 2004 (UT2004 aka UT 2004 aka UT2k4 aka UT 2k4) 10-hour single video HD 1080p playthrough / walkthrough / longplay / gameplay / let's play of the full single player campaign on "Godlike" difficulty. If you would rather watch the same playthrough in 2160p/4K, but in several parts, check out this playlist:

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBWF_Gc9qEJbI4Uwk35xsOmIu__JvMNbt

Difficulty rating 7/10:

https://docs.google.com/file/d/0B_bWv1W6gzNGREQ2RWxNZXBEcGc/edit

For more longplays like this, check out the following playlist:

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBWF_Gc9qEJaAoskC5DG1vhDOGMhBLdrf
